data.message: FYI: Claire Bulat and I had to change the "max results" in the search bar to 100 in order to find the "Twin Cities Fall Retreat" :)
Thanks for the note Alexis! I'm not sure how to change that though :)

message:
FALL RETREAT!!! :) Hi everyone! Here's a reminder to sign-up for Fall Retreat! You need to have a deposit of $25 DOWN by September 28th in order to reserve your spot! 

Register here: https://www.conferenceregistrationtool.com/login.seam?conferenceId=3057&scid=237945

AND - Please make sure you fill out the RIDE LINK when you register. If for some reason you missed it, you can fill it out HERE: 

https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1Jidypuezrf9R-deskbQeAxsO9Zn9s8VcjWRCGRm_GkY/viewform

Remind your friends, too! I am SO EXCITED! 

Let me, David Morelli, Amanda Ann Phillips, or Cody Tucholke know if you have any questions!
